<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_1755675_laptop_0.GetVariableValueUtils</api_name><caller_access>2</caller_access><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><mobile_callable>false</mobile_callable><name>GetVariableValueUtils</name><sandbox_callable>true</sandbox_callable><script><![CDATA[var GetVariableValueUtils = Class.create();
GetVariableValueUtils.prototype = Object.extendsObject(global.AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
    getPreviousValues: function(){
		gs.error('bbbbbbb');
        var sysId = this.getParameter('sysparm_sysId');
        var gr = new GlideRecord('sc_req_item');
        gr.addQuery('number', sysId);
        var result ={};

        gr.query();
        if (gr.next()) {
            result.question1=gr.variables.choose_a_laptop_type +'';
            result.question2=gr.variables.who_need_It +'';
            result.question3=gr.variables.input_your_requirements +'';
            gs.error('gr.variables===========' + result);
            return JSON.stringify(result);
        }else{
            return 'false';
        }
    },
    type: 'GetVariableValueUtils'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-06-12 01:47:32</sys_created_on><sys_id>576c3a06c3c662106a8050e1b40131bc</sys_id><sys_mod_count>10</sys_mod_count><sys_name>GetVariableValueUtils</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Laptop Request" source="x_1755675_laptop_0">337ada5547c22e108762a22f316d43a2</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Laptop Request">337ada5547c22e108762a22f316d43a2</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_576c3a06c3c662106a8050e1b40131bc</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-06-12 04:48:10</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
